INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (57051, 'enUS', 'Centuries ago, this land was still part of the wilds. Reaching the coast was a perilous journey, and many pandaren were lost to the beasts which roam Krasarang, nest of the great crane.$B$BThat is, until the famous hunter Zhu Longbrow came along. Tired of the needless loss of life, Zhu, along with his wife Rin and their son Po - both formidable hunters in their own right - carved out and settled a corner of the wilds.$B$BZhu did not want to settle the wilds entirely, though many begged him to do so. In his wisdom, he understood that they, too, served a purpose: protecting the great crane.$B$BThus Zhu Province was born, and Zhu\'s Watch to protect it.', 'Centuries ago, this land was still part of the wilds. Reaching the coast was a perilous journey, and many pandaren were lost to the beasts which roam Krasarang, nest of the great crane.$B$BThat is, until the famous hunter Zhu Longbrow came along. Tired of the needless loss of life, Zhu, along with his wife Rin and their son Po - both formidable hunters in their own right - carved out and settled a corner of the wilds.$B$BZhu did not want to settle the wilds entirely, though many begged him to do so. In his wisdom, he understood that they, too, served a purpose: protecting the great crane.$B$BThus Zhu Province was born, and Zhu\'s Watch to protect it.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (57052, 'enUS', 'We will make this province safe again. Zhu\'s legacy will not end with this.', 'We will make this province safe again. Zhu\'s legacy will not end with this.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (57053, 'enUS', 'Please tell me about Zhu\'s legacy.', 'Please tell me about Zhu\'s legacy.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (57054, 'enUS', 'Longbrow? Does that mean Yi-Mo is a descendant of Zhu?!', 'Longbrow? Does that mean Yi-Mo is a descendant of Zhu?!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (57055, 'enUS', 'That\'s correct. He is the last remaining member of the Longbrow line.$B$BSadly, he doesn\'t seem to be made of the same stuff as old Zhu. As I\'m sure you noticed, he\'s... dramatic.$B$BPlease do not take this as a sign of weakness: his name and the responsibilities that come along with it weigh on him heavily. I know Yi-Mo only wants what is best for the province.$B$BSome day he will come to understand that, at times, you must fight for what you love.', 'That\'s correct. He is the last remaining member of the Longbrow line.$B$BSadly, he doesn\'t seem to be made of the same stuff as old Zhu. As I\'m sure you noticed, he\'s... dramatic.$B$BPlease do not take this as a sign of weakness: his name and the responsibilities that come along with it weigh on him heavily. I know Yi-Mo only wants what is best for the province.$B$BSome day he will come to understand that, at times, you must fight for what you love.', 26124);
